---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Window Replacement Hampton Park | Aluminium & Double-Glaze | (03) 9003 0108"
  description="Window replacement across Hampton Park 3976 — 1980s–90s brick-veneer aluminium swap-outs, double-glaze upgrades for the cold valley winters, sliding-door upgrades for ex-rental tidy-ups."
  canonical="https://berwickwindowreplacement.com.au/hampton-park/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Hampton Park 3976</span>
      <h1>Window replacement in <span class="accent">Hampton Park</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Hampton Park is one of the oldest growth-corridor suburbs in southern
        Casey &mdash; built out heavily in the late 1970s and 80s, with a
        second wave of estate infill in the 90s. The aluminium and steel
        windows from that era are well past their working life: corner-rust on
        the steel casements, perished gaskets on the aluminium, single panes
        that frost up overnight in winter.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book a free measure</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Hampton Park</span>
      <h2>The Hampton Park window story.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Oldest growth-corridor stock in Casey.</h3>
        <p>
          Hampton Park dates the housing back to the late 70s and 80s.
          You&rsquo;ll see steel-frame windows in some of the original
          estate homes &mdash; these are at the end of their working life,
          rusting at the corners, hard to operate, single-paned. Slightly
          newer 90s homes have early-spec aluminium, also single-glazed and
          chalky. Both are full frame replacement, not glass-only or
          sash-only.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Cold valley winters &mdash; condensation is the giveaway.</h3>
        <p>
          Hampton Park sits in a slightly cooler valley pocket than Berwick
          &mdash; cold air drains down off the higher land overnight and
          settles. The condensation problem on single-glaze windows is
          worse here than further north: glass surface temperatures of
          3&ndash;4&deg;C are normal on a July morning. Double-glazing
          lifts that to 12&ndash;14&deg;C and the condensation stops
          forming. We push double-glazing harder here than in
          Cranbourne East &mdash; the payback in Hampton Park is faster
          because you&rsquo;re heating against more cold-loss hours per
          year.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Ex-rental tidy-ups for sale.</h3>
        <p>
          Lots of Hampton Park stock has been investor-owned and rented
          for 10&ndash;20 years; when owners sell, they call us to
          replace tired windows and the back sliding door so the house
          presents properly. We can stage a 3&ndash;4 day full re-window
          + slider replacement before listing for $11K&ndash;$16K &mdash;
          adds $25K&ndash;$40K to the sale price for the kind of stock
          that&rsquo;s otherwise getting buyer-discounted on the
          condition.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Hampton Park jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Full-house re-window, 11&ndash;14 windows ($11K&ndash;$16K)</li>
          <li>Double-glaze upgrade across full house ($15K&ndash;$20K)</li>
          <li>Steel-frame rust-out replacement (per window $700&ndash;$1,400)</li>
          <li>Pre-sale tidy-up: windows + back slider, 3 days on site ($12K&ndash;$17K)</li>
          <li>Single bathroom or laundry awning emergency swap ($550&ndash;$900)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/berwick/">Berwick</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/cranbourne/">Cranbourne</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/narre-warren/">Narre Warren</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/endeavour-hills/">Endeavour Hills</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/city-of-casey/">All City of Casey</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Hampton Park window measure-up.</h2>
        <p>Pre-sale tidy-ups, double-glaze winter-comfort upgrades, rust-out steel-frame replacements.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
